10. Sky module
--------------
Replaced the IDL based World Coordinate System code by wcslib based code.
This improves performance and accuracy of the coordinate transformation
and corrects a bug in the LONPOLE/LATPOLE keywords that were written in
the earlier version into the FITS file.
Introduced GWcslib base class for projections that are wcslib based.
All code adapted from wcslib goes into that class. Not all functionality
has yet been ported from wcslib to GammaLib, but the essential things
for creating, writing and reading WCS compliant FITS files is there.
Introduced a World Coordinate System registry for easy extension of the
set of projections.


